ANGELS VS. TAMPA BAY
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By JOE HAAKENSON  
 c.1999 San Gabriel Valley Tribune  
 
__ Time: 7:35 p.m. at Edison Field. 
__ TV/Radio: FSW; KLAC-570, XPRS-1090. 
__ Matchup: Jarrod Washburn (2-4, 6.00 ERA) will start for Anaheim
against Tampa Bay's Dan Wheeler (0-2, 5.49). Tonight's game is the
final game of the homestand. After three in Seattle, the Angels
return home for their final six games of the season _ three against
