<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-09-22 11:58 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1385 &Cx1f; taf-z
u a BC-CPT-WEB-RATINGS-NYT &LR;      09-22 1083
