<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-09-22 13:22 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1533 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u s BC-GLF-RYDER-ROOTS-2TAKE     09-22 1593
