TV-GOODY (Undated) _ Remember the ``Seinfeld'' episode where
Jerry's landlord installed low-flow shower heads? And Jerry and
Kramer spent much of the broadcast with flat hair? That's an apt
way to talk about Thursday night television. We're still musing
about ``Seinfeld``; otherwise, things have fallen flat. Must-see
TV? Hardly. This is America. You can watch whatever you want. By
BILL GOODYKOONTZ. Story will move in the ``E'' category. &QL; 
