   (NYT43) NEW YORK -- Sept. 22, 1999 -- GOODALL-PROFILE, 09-22 --
Jane Goodall, the British primatologist, is raising money for seven
chimp sanctuaries in Africa. For the last 13 years, she has never
been in one place more than four weeks. (Librado Romero/New York
Times Photo)
</P>
