   A New York Times News Service article sent on Wednesday, Sept.
15, about consumer rebates in the computer industry misidentified
the software for which Ann-Marie Carpenter of Gilmanton, N.H., was
unable to redeem a rebate coupon. It was Print Artist Platinum 4.5,
published by Sierra Home, not Printmaster Gold, by the Learning
Company.
